{"word":"ἐχυρός","slug":"ἐχυρός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐχυρός</b></el> <el>(ἐχῠρός, ή, όν) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><el>ἔχω</el>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>strong, secure</i>, of Places, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>; <el>ἐν ἐχυρῷ εἶναι</el> to be <i>in safety</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>; <el>ἐν ἐχυρωτάτῳ ποιεῖσθαί τι</el> <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>of reasons, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>, <i>trustworthy</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a> <el>-ρῶς</el>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>; <a href='S:Comparative'>comp.</a> <el>-ώτερον</el>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}